In a medium pan, bring water to a boil. Add tea bags, and remove pan from heat. Allow tea to steep, about 3 minutes. Remove tea bags, and let water cool completely. In a large bowl, mix together frozen orange juice concentrate, frozen lemonade concentrate, apricot brandy and cooled tea. Freeze mixture 12 to 24 hours. Ladle brandy shush into glasses, and top with a splash of lemon-lime flavored soda.